    </name>
    <questiontext format="moodle_auto_format">
      <text><![CDATA[<p>

John invested $5,000 in a small business. After 2 years, the value of his investment appreciated at an annual rate of 8%. However, in the following year, the business was affected by a recession and the value depreciated by 12%.</p><p>

a) Calculate the value of the investment after the appreciation period.</p><p>
b) Calculate the final value of the investment after the depreciation.</p><p>
c) State whether John made a profit or a loss, and by how much.</p><p>
d) Express the overall percentage change in value over the entire 3-year period.</p><p>[[input:ans1]] [[validation:ans1]]</p>]]></text>
    </questiontext>
